title: quarkus-amazon-services fails to build
body:

building quarkus-amazon-services fails in in io.quarkiverse.amazon.s3.deployment.DevServicesWithComposeDevServicesTest

### Expected behavior

The build should complete successfully

1. Check out quarkus-amazon-services from github
2. Ensure docker is running
3. build the project using `mvn clean install -Dquickly -Dskip.gradle.tests -Dskip.gradle.build`
